reviewText: This is a magical journey one takes to discover the passion, love and grace of a woman destined to take you to a great place within yourself. Karen inspires everyone she meets either in person or when she speaks. She moves mountains with her words but even stronger, she moves our spirits and souls to feel hope and to feel that we can all make something great in our lives. You must buy this video and share it with your friends and watch it with your children or bring it to your schools.
